data.description: Check out this 3-Bedroom 2-Bath spacious floor plan located on 0.69-acre of land in the rapidly developing area of East Palmetto. NO HOA, NO CDD, and NO Flood Zone provides endless opportunities with NO restrictions.   EXTERIOR FEATURES INCLUDE: Fully fenced in yard with secured entry gate, 2-car detached garage (720 SF), large driveway provides amble room for multiple vehicles with TONS of additional space to accommodate an RV, Boat, ATV and other toys! INTERIOR FEATURES INCLUDE: tile flooring throughout (NO CARPET), Separate Dining Room off of the Kitchen offers newer SS Appliances (2022), Split floor plan, Guests have their own full Bathroom with Shower/Tub Combo,  and Master Bedroom/en suite with direct access to Laundry Room. Updated Features: HVAC (2021), Roof (2016), Washer & Dryer (2022), Lighting (2022) and newly updated Kitchen and Bathrooms.   Conveniently located to I-75 & I-275 for commutes to Tampa, St Pete or Sarasota/Bradenton area.  Minutes from Dining, Banking, Groceries and best of all the Ellenton Outlet Mall. Less than 10-minute drive to public boat ramp that provides access to the Manatee River as well as the Gulf of Mexico. For trips to our beautiful beaches, you are less than 30-minute drive to St. Pete or Anna Maria Island.
